# oauth
OAuth library for nim

OAuth is composed of two modules.
Please read documentation for details.

- [oauth1](http://cordea.github.io/oauth/docs/oauth1.html)
- [oauth2](http://cordea.github.io/oauth/docs/oauth2.html)
